      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "我们的大脑靠上千亿个神经元互相传递信号来思考。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "人工神经网络，正是对这套机制的一次大胆模仿。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "今天我们就跟着一个信号，看它如何在网络里层层流动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "neuron",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "neuron-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/neuron-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "每个神经元先把上一层的输入乘上各自的权重，再全部加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "neuron",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "neuron-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/neuron-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "加上一个偏置后，得到一个总和，我们叫它加权和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "neuron",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "neuron-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/neuron-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "这个和再经过激活函数，就成了这个神经元的输出。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "propagate",
      "line_id": "prop-1",
      "filename": "propagate-prop-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/propagate-prop-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "一层的输出，会成为下一层每个神经元的输入。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "propagate",
      "line_id": "prop-2",
      "filename": "propagate-prop-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/propagate-prop-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "就这样从左到右，信号一层接一层地被重新加工。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "propagate",
      "line_id": "prop-3",
      "filename": "propagate-prop-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/propagate-prop-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "走到最后的输出层，网络就给出了它的答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "activation",
      "line_id": "act-1",
      "filename": "activation-act-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/activation-act-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "sigmoid 把任何数都压进零到一之间，像一个平滑的开关。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "activation",
      "line_id": "act-2",
      "filename": "activation-act-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/activation-act-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "若只做加权求和，再多层也只是一条直线的组合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "activation",
      "line_id": "act-3",
      "filename": "activation-act-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/activation-act-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "正是激活函数的非线性，让网络能拟合弯弯曲曲的复杂规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "切换不同的输入，观察每个神经元的亮度如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "亮起的强弱，就是信号在这一层被放大或抑制的痕迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "神经元做加权求和加偏置，再过激活函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/neural-network-forward/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "信号逐层前向传播，最终汇成网络的输出。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "neural-network-forward",
      "section_id": "summary",
